---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
const datum = "30 June 2026";
---

<SiteLayout
  locale="en"
  title="Cookies and Local Storage | VinoMartino"
  description="What VinoMartino stores in your browser and which third parties make a connection."
  alternates={{ nl: '/cookies/', en: '/en/cookies/' }}
>
  <section class="legal container">
    <article class="legal-body">
      <h1>Cookies and Local Storage</h1>
      <p class="update-datum"><em>Last updated: {datum}</em></p>

      <p>VinoMartino does not display a cookie banner. Below we explain what is stored in your browser and which third parties make a connection.</p>

      <h2>Functional local storage (first-party)</h2>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>What</th><th>Technology</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Commercial?</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Theme preference (light/dark)</td><td><code>localStorage</code> (your browser)</td><td>Remembering visual setting</td><td>No</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>We do not place any first-party tracking cookies.</p>

      <h2>First-party click tracking for affiliate links</h2>
      <p>When you click an affiliate link, we send an anonymous click signal to our own server (<code>/api/clicks/affiliate</code>). This contains: the link type, the partner platform, the page you clicked on and the timestamp. No name, email address or IP address.</p>

      <h2>Third parties: what loads when</h2>

      <p><em>On page load (before any click):</em></p>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Script / connection</th><th>What it does</th><th>Sets a cookie?</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Stay22 <code>letmeallez.js</code> (from <code>scripts.stay22.com</code>)</td><td>Rewrites accommodation links client-side so they run via Stay22; may display an overlay</td><td><strong>No</strong>, makes a network connection but places no tracking/attribution cookie on load</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Plausible Analytics (from <code>plausible.io</code>)</td><td>Cookie-free visitor statistics; stores no personal data or IP addresses</td><td><strong>No</strong>, places no cookies and uses no local storage</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p><em>Only when clicking through to a partner link:</em></p>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Partner</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Stay22 / Booking.com</td><td>Accommodation booking and commission attribution</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Booking.com via Commission Junction</td><td>Booking processing and commission attribution</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Sunny Cars via TradeTracker</td><td>Car rental booking and commission attribution</td></tr>
          <tr><td>GetYourGuide</td><td>Tasting tickets, tours and commission attribution</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>When you click through to one of these partners, further data processing falls under their own privacy policy.</p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Clear local storage:</strong> via browser settings → Privacy → Site data. Only your theme preference will be removed.</li>
        <li><strong>Block the Stay22 script:</strong> via a content blocker. The text content of the site works normally; Stay22's accommodation link optimisation will be disabled.</li>
        <li><strong>Opt out of analytics:</strong> via browser extensions such as uBlock Origin or via Google's opt-out: <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>See our <a href="/en/privacy/">Privacy policy</a> or email <a href="mailto:privacy@vinomartino.com">privacy@vinomartino.com</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
  }
  .legal-body {
    max-width: 44rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .legal-body h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.6rem + 1.5vw, 2.875rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .legal-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: var(--space-10) 0 var(--space-3);
  }
  .legal-body p,
  .legal-body ul {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--inkSoft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .legal-body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-body li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .legal-body a {
    color: var(--burgundy);
  }
  .legal-body a:hover {
    color: var(--burgundyDeep);
  }
  .legal-body strong {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .update-datum {
    color: var(--inkFaint);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-6);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }
  th {
    background: var(--paperDeep);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  td {
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ruleSoft);
    color: var(--inkSoft);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  code {
    background: var(--paperDeep);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
